        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "123.Trong has 12% of each paycheck automatically deposited to his savings account. His last paycheck was $2,165. How much money was deposited to Trong's savings account?",
        "bbox": [
          0.5670588235294117,
